{{Infobox film festival | name = Hainan International Film Festival | logo = Hainan International Film Festival logo.jpg | logo_alt = | logo_size = | image = | image_alt = | image_size = | caption = | opening = | closing = | location = [[Sanya]], Hainan, China | founded = {{start date and age|2018|12|9|df=yes}} | disestablished = | successor = | awardsreceived = | awards = | films = | directors = | producers = | writers = | starring = | host = | number = | date = | language = | website = {{URL|http://www.hndiff.com/index_en.html}} (English) | chronology = | preceded_by = | followed_by = }} The '''Hainan International Film Festival''' ({{zh|s=海南岛国际电影节}}) is an upcoming film festival to be held in [[Sanya]], Hainan, China.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gbtimes.com/first-international-film-festival-to-be-held-in-the-chinese-tropical-province-of-hainan|title=First international film festival to be held in the Chinese tropical province of Hainan|website=GBTIMES}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ehainan.gov.cn/2018-11/13/c_290987.htm|title=Intl film festival to debut in Hainan|website=www.ehainan.gov.cn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinesefilms.cn/141/2018/11/14/281s26623.htm|title=Hainan to hold first int'l film festival in December - Chinese Films|website=www.chinesefilms.cn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2018-11/12/c_137601549.htm|title=Hainan to hold first int'l film festival in December - Xinhua - English.news.cn|website=www.xinhuanet.com}}</ref> The inaugural festival will be held from December 9 to 16, and will include forums, ceremonies, and competitions. Actor Jackie Chan is the intended promotional ambassador.
